.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH dkp-init 1  "init 0.1.2" 
.SH NAME
dkp\-init \- Scaffold a new DKP pack directory with all required files
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdkp init\fR <\fB\-\-domain\fR> [\fB\-\-output\fR] [\fB\-\-out\fR] [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-\-extras\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-\-audience\fR] [\fB\-\-force\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fINAME\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Scaffold a new DKP pack directory with all required files
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-domain\fR \fI<DOMAIN>\fR
Top\-level domain category (e.g. "Health", "Finance")
.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR \fI<OUTPUT>\fR [default: plain]
Output format
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
plain: Human\-readable plain text (default)
.IP \(bu 2
table: Aligned table using comfy\-table
.IP \(bu 2
json: Pretty\-printed JSON
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-out\fR \fI<OUT>\fR
Output directory (default: ./<name\-slug>/)
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress informational output; print only results
.TP
\fB\-\-extras\fR
Also scaffold optional recommended assets: eval_set.jsonl, knowledge_graph.json, human/handbook.md, README.md, CHANGELOG.md
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Print debug info (schema paths, provider calls, etc.)
.TP
\fB\-\-audience\fR \fI<ID>\fR
Filter content to assets tagged for a specific audience profile
.TP
\fB\-\-force\fR
Overwrite if directory already exists
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.TP
<\fINAME\fR>
Pack name (e.g. "Nutrition for Men")
.SH VERSION
v0.1.2
